name: Fun way to be Happy #2
description:
Have yourself eat healthy food is another key of Happiness. Eating a variety of foods and consuming less salt, sugars and saturated and industrially-produced trans-fats, are essential for healthy digest, mind and soul.

The rights that I could give to those of you who are willing to collect this work:
- You can print this work into poster or any other wall decoration and display on your house, workspace, or even on your restaurant. You can DM me for the High Resolution Image.
- You can share this work on any Social Media with the aim of providing information that you had collect and enjoy my work.
